title: Project,chalices, 1914–20
medium: Pencil, white heightening, watercolor, cardboard with gray obverse (split)
signed: Signed similar to 1939-84-75-a,b,d with added: Mass
description: Vertical rectangle. Bordering line as 1939-84-20. In Gothic style. Round foot with the synbols of the Evangelists and a cross, in quatrefoils. Gems at the knob.
